{"tid":860321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明天放下成見、放下私怨","createTime":"2018-10-13T09:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T17:07:26.000Z","uid":129622,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f81e4a349fc6701eac08a55e9514046866a2d26a","tid":860321,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:00:25.000Z","msg":"四年後今日有一次咁重要既機會，無謂為抗爭形式、立場、私怨而浪費今次機會<br />\n執著和平形象、道德高地，你唔會係極權之下爭取到任何權益<br />\n相反未掌握到足夠抗爭者動員支持，無計劃地盲目衝擊，結果亦只會成為甕中捉鱉<br />\n<br />\n最大機會成功只有各派各有各做，唔好再開記招割席，亦唔好攻擊人唱歌畫畫<br />\n成功爭取合理權益前，決不讓步散水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b33effe21c170482fc634cd04abbb462d20b289","tid":860321,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3e278d2fd4dd827e752319e38849221a6939ed","tid":860321,"uid":16846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:01:30.000Z","msg":"你會放，但搞嗰個唔會放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6cdc86c8b2e1adf99c658fcdfa0d85cc22e4a2","tid":860321,"uid":129622,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"be3e278d2fd4dd827e752319e38849221a6939ed","tid":860321,"uid":16846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:01:30.000Z","msg":"你會放，但搞嗰個唔會放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T12:49:35.000Z","msg":"仲好記得當日邵家臻囂張嘴臉，同學聯無計劃吹雞害死一班抗爭者，就算但再討厭佢地，聽日衡量過有需要都會幫手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00150fa3ba0e6f0ded1a1aa7ea0543a676fdefaa","tid":860321,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"留名睇50人加佔中正式啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7c7018b53c94c3c312ff6534a72556c538e329","tid":860321,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":